<!--Display _header.ejs partial-->
<%- include("./partials/_header.ejs")  %>

<!--Display a main container-->
<div class="main-container">
    <!--Display an upper grid container-->
    <div class="upper">
        <!--Display a _header and information about Pets-R-Us-->
        <h1>Our Mission:</h1>
        <p class="summary">Here at Pets-R-Us, our goal is to be the one-stop-shop for pet owners in the Tri-Cities area. 
           We pride ourselves in meeting the needs of our customers and their pets, which is why we offer
           high quality products from only the hottest brands that will keep your four-legged friend happy 
           and healthy at prices that owners will love.<br><br>Our new dog grooming and boarding services are run
           by professionals that care deeply about the needs of each dog, we promise that owners will be 
           satisfied with the level of care that we have to offer, or your money back. Whether you've got a dog, cat,
