            <p>Mon: 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM</p>
            <p>Tue: 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM</p>
            <p>Wed: 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM</p>
            <p>Thu: 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM</p>
            <p>Fri: 8:00 AM - 9:00 PM</p>
            <p>Sat: 8:00 AM - 9:00 PM</p>
            <p>Sun: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

